I have a love/hate relationship with speed days. 🏃‍♀️Today’s session:

1mi warm up
4min hard, 2min easy X6
For 4min hard not a sprint but a strong push.
Cool down to 6mi 

I hit a solid 9 min pace for the 4 min hard. Even pushed it to 8:45. I felt great on the other side of it. What’s your thoughts on speed days? 🤔
